    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This example demonstrates impeccable mechanical health with a recently serviced dual-VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe. The S54 powerplant retains its factory-spec compression ratios and features individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Power is managed via the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a GKN limited-slip differential. The suspension has been meticulously maintained with OEM-spec components, preserving the chassis's legendary torsional rigidity and 50/50 balance. This is a collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance and a pristine undercarriage.",
