      "description": "Presented in absolute showroom condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero chips or imperfections, protected by a recent professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent, featuring supple, uncreased leather upholstery and a dashboard completely free of UV wear or micro-scratches. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a complete portfolio of meticulous service records performed exclusively at authorized centers. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. Fitted with brand-new premium tires on unmarked alloy wheels, this car delivers a tight, quiet, and powerful driving experience identical to its first day on the road. This is a turnkey opportunity to own a truly immaculate, investment-grade specimen.",
