    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and a linear 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable: the dual-VANOS timing system has been fully serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to exceed factory structural rigidness. With zero oil seepage from the valve cover gasket and a cooling system overhaul already completed, this specimen offers turn-key performance for the discerning collector. The chassis remains taut, preserving the sharp turn-in and balanced kinematics that define this platform.",
